scaled.jpg 1717w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-5-728x933.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-5-768x984.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-5-1199x1536.jpg 1199w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-5-1598x2048.jpg 1598w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-5-150x192.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1717px) 100vw, 1717px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201717%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-5-scaled.jpg 1717w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-5-728x933.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-5-768x984.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-5-1199x1536.jpg 1199w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-5-1598x2048.jpg 1598w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-5-150x192.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-5-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe smoked turkey sausage is an ingredient that I’m always looking to use in new and exciting ways. We love\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2018/04/sheet-pan-sausage-peppers/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003e the classic sheet pan meal with peppers\u003c/a\u003e, or \u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2024/09/sheet-pan-smoked-sausage-tortellini/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003ewith tortellini\u003c/a\u003e. I also love \u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2024/02/smoked-sausage-potato-soup/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eto use it in soup\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2023/04/grilled-smoked-sausage-skewers/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003estuffed on grilled skewers\u003c/a\u003e!\u003cspan id=\"more-97605\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-7-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"sheet pan pierogi, smoked sausage and brussels sprouts\" width=\"1732\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Sheet Pan Pierogi, Smoked Sausage \u0026amp; Brussels Sprouts.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-7-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-7-scaled.jpg 1732w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-7-728x924.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-7-768x975.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-7-1210x1536.jpg 1210w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-7-1613x2048.jpg 1613w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-7-150x190.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1732px) 100vw, 1732px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201732%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-7-scaled.jpg 1732w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-7-728x924.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-7-768x975.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-7-1210x1536.jpg 1210w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-7-1613x2048.jpg 1613w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-7-150x190.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-7-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAll three of these have tons of flavor on their own, making them great for a sheet pan meal. These isn’t much extra work to do because roasting takes care of it with that charred, caramely goodness.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe best part!\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-8-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"sheet pan pierogi, smoked sausage and brussels sprouts\" width=\"1560\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Sheet Pan Pierogi, Smoked Sausage \u0026amp; Brussels Sprouts.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-8-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-8-scaled.jpg 1560w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-8-728x1027.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-8-768x1083.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-8-1089x1536.jpg 1089w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/s