ps://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-11-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-11-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-11-96x96.jpg 96w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20200%20200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-11-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-11-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-11-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-11-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-11-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-11-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-11-96x96.jpg 96w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-11-250x250.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eSheet Pan Pierogies, Smoked Sausage \u0026amp; Brussels Sprouts\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" width=\"16px\" height=\"16px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cg\u003e\u003cpath fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M10,0C9.4,0,9,0.4,9,1v4H7V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S5,0.4,5,1v4H3V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S1,0.4,1,1v8c0,1.7,1.3,3,3,3v10c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V12c1.7,0,3-1.3,3-3V1C11,0.4,10.6,0,10,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003cpath data-color=\"color-2\" fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M19,0c-3.3,0-6,2.7-6,6v9c0,0.6,0.4,1,1,1h2v6c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V1C20,0.4,19.6,0,19,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/g\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eYield: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan data-recipe=\"97619\" aria-label=\"Adjust recipe servings\"\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eto 4\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePrep Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e10\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCook Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e30\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTotal Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e40\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\t\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis sheet pan sausage and pierogi meal is a huge hit! Smoked sausage, your favorite variety of pierogi and brussels sprouts are roasted until charred and soft with sautéed onions. Delicious and so easy!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"97619\" data-servings=\"2\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003elarge sweet onion,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ethinly sliced\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e3\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/pure-olive-oil-25-5oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-77600361?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eolive oil\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/balsamic-vinegar-of-modena-16-9oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-83863106?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ebalsamic vinegar\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ekosher salt and pepper\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"7\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1/2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/garlic-powder-3-12oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-77585075?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003egarlic powder\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e16\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eounces\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003efrozen or refrigerated pierogi\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"5\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e16\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eoz\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003esmoked sausage,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecut into rounds\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"6\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e8\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eounces\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/brussels-sprouts-12oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-54535942?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ebrussels sprouts,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003equartered\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"97619\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97619-step-0-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003ePreheat the oven to 425 degrees F. Spray a baking sheet with nonstick spray or drizzle with olive oil.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97619-step-0-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePlace the onions on one side of the sheet, then the brussels in the center. Place the sausage on the other side. Drizzle the onions, brussels and sausage with 2 tablespoons of olive oil. Sprinkle salt and pepper all over. Sprinkle with garlic powder.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97619-step-0-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eDrizzle the onions and brussels with the balsamic vinegar. Toss if needed to coat.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97619-step-0-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eLay the pierogi on top of the onions. Drizzle with the remaining olive oil and sprinkle with salt and pepper.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97619-step-0-4\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eRoast for 15 to 20 minutes, then flip everything (especially the pierogi!) and roast for 10 to 15 minutes more.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97619-step-0-5\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eRemove from the oven and let cool slightly before serving.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCourse: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMain Course\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCuisine: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAmerican\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-10-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"sheet pan pierogi, sausage and brussels sprouts\" width=\"1716\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Sheet Pan Pierogi, Smoked Sausage \u0026amp; Brussels Sprouts.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-10-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-10-scaled.jpg 1716w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-10-728x933.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sheet-pan-sausage-and-pierogi-10-768x985.jpg 76